briefdescription.para: CMSIS Cortex-M0+ Device Peripheral Access Layer Header File. This file contains all the peripheral register's definitions, bits definitions and memory mapping for stm32g030xx devices.

detaileddescription.para:
MCD Application Team
This file contains:
Data structures and the address mapping for all peripherals
Peripheral's registers declarations and bits definition
Macros to access peripheral's registers hardware
